        <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-4">Our Environmental Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-5">We aim to build a clean infrastructure where not a single circuit board is burned in fields or dumped in water. Our specific goals align with the UN Sustainable Development Goal 12 (Responsible Consumption & Production).</p>
        
        <div class="row g-4 text-start">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 card-hover">
